snippet.title: MagicToMaster Official Cinematic
snippet.description:
MagicToMaster (shortly M2M) is a Massively Multiplayer Online Role-Playing Game
Originally developed by #Laniatus Games and originally released in Hungary in 2014. 
Since then, different versions have been published by #Laniatus Games in many European countries and the United States. Other versions are available in Hungarian.

First release date: 2014
Developer: #Laniatus
Publishers: #Laniatus
Platforms: Microsoft Windows, GeForce Now
Genres: Massively multiplayer online role-playing game, Free to play, Action game, Massively Multiplayer, Adventure

https://www.laniatusgames.com
https://www.magictomaster.org
https://www.magictomaster.net
